Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.01,0:00:08.98,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Wow. Are there always this many people here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:11.29,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,This is actually on the sparse side.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.29,0:00:12.24,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,This crowd?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:17.21,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,I've only ever heard about it from people \Nwho came to the shop, but this is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:20.24,Italics,SHIN/ID,0,0,0,,She's like a child visiting \Nan amusement park for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:23.14,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Don't get lost because \Nyou're having too much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:25.88,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,I-I'm not {\i1}that{\i0} excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:28.44,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Let's complete our errands first.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:32.06,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Then we can use our remaining time\N however we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:36.23,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,You're right. Okay, let's head to the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:45.91,Italics,SHIN/ID,0,0,0,,I'd hardly believe she used \Nto be afraid to go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.22,0:00:50.78,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,By the way, do you know where the guild is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:53.30,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:00:55.70,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:56.95,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
