Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:53.01,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What? But I still haven't \Ncompleted a single job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:03:01.16,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,You defeated a high-ranking Skullface \Nand a surprise horde of Skullfaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:06.16,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,The guild has verified your reports,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:10.21,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,so we've decided to promote you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:12.54,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:16.73,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,Personally, I think you could've \Nbeen promoted to rank A.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:21.13,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Other adventurers wouldn't look kindly \Non such a big promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:26.70,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,By the way, how do you know this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:30.33,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,We're traveling together on mutual business.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:32.37,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Since we were stopping by anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:36.07,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I thought she could register as \Nan adventurer and get a guild card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:38.07,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,Is she your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:38.98,Default,BOTH,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:40.32,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,N-N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:42.96,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,I heard you were holding hands like a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:45.82,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,H-How did you find out about that so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:50.45,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,She's certainly beautiful. \NMen just can't help themselves, can they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:53.54,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Why do you sound so hostile?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:59.11,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,Holding hands with a pretty woman\Nmust feel like some kind of dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:04.04,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,Even if you end up ogling her around town, \Nit's nothing to be ashamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:06.04,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,You can't help it, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.60,Italics,SHIN/ID,0,0,0,,Uh-oh. We've triggered something weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:13.81,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Um, by the way, do you have \Nany information on sacred sites?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.10,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,Sacred sites?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:19.41,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yeah, the places said to have been destroyed\Nduring the Dusk of Prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:26.74,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but we can't disclose information \Non those to anyone below rank B.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:30.94,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I see. I was mostly just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:33.53,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'll come back once I've ranked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:35.50,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I know. I'm going to Farnid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:39.60,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Do you have any jobs \NI could complete on the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.01,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:46.93,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,Let's see. In the direction of Farnid...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:51.64,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,Someone is requesting a wagon escort \Nto Bayreun's staging post.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:51.64,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\bord3\fs20\an7\c&H2E3435&\3c&HCFDBE0&\4c&HCFDBE0&\b1}Job Description: Wagon escort to Bayreun\N Client: Nakk\NOpen Positions: Up to five\N Reward: Ten silver coins per person
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:53.59,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:55.53,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What do you think, Tiera?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:57.33,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,It's certainly fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.52,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:02.99,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,They're departing this afternoon \Nwhen the bell rings thrice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:07.30,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,Two adventurers have already signed on,\N so please meet up with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:13.69,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,We've got some time \Nuntil my guild card is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:16.54,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,We're not getting together\Nfor the job until the afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:20.40,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,so let's wander through town \Non our way to the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.45,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:54.61,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Lacia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:57.33,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Hey there. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:06:00.46,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,Good morning, Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.83,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,And... who might this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:08.09,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,My name is Tiera. It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:10.05,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:14.35,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,I am Lacia, a nun at this church.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:16.84,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,I work at the Moon Sanctum—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:18.69,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,What? The Moon Sanctum?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:21.58,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,Does that mean you know Schnee?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:23.49,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,She's my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:24.36,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:26.42,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,That's incredible! Just incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:28.36,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,How did you become her student?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:31.12,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,Is Schnee a strict master?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:35.26,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,In your opinion, what kind of person is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:38.17,Default,MILLIE,0,0,0,,Good to see you, Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:41.54,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You seem well, Millie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:46.02,Default,MILLIE,0,0,0,,Yeah. The orphanage \Nis here to stay 'cause of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:47.38,Default,MILLIE,0,0,0,,Thanks, Shin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.13,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Really? That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:56.24,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I'll be taking over\Nas the next head of the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:58.52,Default,TRIA,0,0,0,,The children are delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:00.82,Default,TRIA,0,0,0,,We don't know how to repay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.17,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:05.02,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Actually, where's Wilhelm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:07.97,Default,TRIA,0,0,0,,He's investigating the other priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:11.13,Default,TRIA,0,0,0,,He said there's no way \Nthat man would back down quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:13.37,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,That figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:18.41,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,After all, we still don't know why \Nthis guy wanted to take over the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:21.48,Default,TRIA,0,0,0,,I hope it's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:24.29,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Take this just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:25.63,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You too, Millie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:27.30,Default,MILLIE,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:30.17,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It's enchanted with all kinds of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:32.09,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Think of it as a lucky charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:33.18,Default,MILLIE,0,0,0,,A lucky charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:36.46,Default,TRIA,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:38.21,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:39.20,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:42.33,Default,CHILD 1,0,0,0,,Sister, is it true that Shin is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:43.81,Default,CHILD 2,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:46.85,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Hey, guys. You look full of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.33,Default,CHILD 1,0,0,0,,We are, we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:50.29,Default,CHILD 2,0,0,0,,Play with us, Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:51.95,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I've got treats for you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:52.94,Default,CHILD 4,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:54.38,Default,CHILD 1,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:56.45,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Shin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:59.62,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:04.89,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I only left you for a second,\Nand they've taken right to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:10.96,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for the fuss the children caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:12.05,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Oh, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:16.86,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,I was unsure at first since I've\Nnever played with children before,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:19.06,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,but they're so lively and cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:22.94,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,Indeed. I swear I'll protect this pwace—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:24.89,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:32.19,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,This is your guild card, Tiera.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:33.70,Default,CELICA,0,0,0,,Please look it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:36.57,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an8\shad0\fs14\fnArial\b1\3c&H4E483E&\u1}Guild Card{\u0}\N{\fs16}Tiera\N{\fs14}Adventurer Rank G
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:39.14,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Now I'm an adventurer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:41.86,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Let's go pick up the Moon Sanctum next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.24,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,I'd completely forgotten about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:46.78,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,That's the last thing you should forget about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:49.59,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Carrying your house around with you \Nis crazy in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:56.09,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Huh. Since I own the Moon Sanctum,\N it just seems totally normal to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:08:59.60,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Is that a crystal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:03.97,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,I've never seen one so large \Nand beautifully refined before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:07.39,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It's enchanted with the Teleport spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:11.48,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It's a consumable item that instantly \Nwarps you to a saved location.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:14.75,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Let's use this to get to the Moon Sanctum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:19.02,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,I swear, everything you pull out\Nof your pocket is something extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:22.49,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you can make these too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:27.87,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What? How are crystals enchanted \Nwith Teleport treated these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:31.05,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Teleportation is a lost spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:34.06,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,As long as I have the materials, \NI can make as many as I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:35.63,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Sorry, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:40.37,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Of course you can. \NYou're a legendary high human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:46.73,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,The coast is clear. Welp, all ready to warp?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:48.65,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Yes. Go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:50.45,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.16,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\b1\shad0\fs10\t(\fs9)\c&HD0DAED&\3c&H5B6F8A&)\pos(320,174.571)}Moon Sanctum
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:06.48,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Wow. What a strange feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:08.20,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:09.67,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,What? Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:13.80,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Storage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:28.63,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.37,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:34.57,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yup. This is the Moon Sanctum \Nin transport mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:37.61,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:42.57,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Okay, we've finished all our errands.\NShall we head to the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:50.65,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:53.84,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Is this Nakk's wagon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:58.57,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,That's right. Are you also \Nadventurers who took the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:01.72,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yes. We'll be joining you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:04.14,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'm Shin. This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:06.60,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,I'm Tiera. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:11.28,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,I'm Gaien. I look forward\N to traveling with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.19,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,And this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:18.65,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,Tsubaki. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:20.97,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yeah. Nice to meet you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:22.13,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:24.62,Default,NAKK,0,0,0,,Okay, looks like everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:27.02,Default,NAKK,0,0,0,,I'm Nakk the merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:29.12,Default,NAKK,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you to get me to Bayreun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:31.10,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:42.01,Default,NAKK,0,0,0,,All aboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:44.26,Default,NAKK,0,0,0,,Then we're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:54.02,Default,JAYON,0,0,0,,The Moon Sanctum has disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:56.05,Default,JAYON,0,0,0,,You're absolutely certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:59.40,Default,CHANCELLOR,0,0,0,,Yes. The reports are correct, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:05.41,Default,JAYON,0,0,0,,An immovable structure\Nthat survived the Dusk of Prosperity...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:17.42,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(980,980)\fnTimes New Roman\b1\fay-.05\shad0\fs13\t(\fs10)\c&HD0DAED&\3c&H2B3D47&\move(262.286,210.286,276,202.143)}Moon Sanctum
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:13.16,Default,JAYON,0,0,0,,Not even the most powerful individuals \Nor high-level monsters could break into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:16.47,Default,JAYON,0,0,0,,A mystical shop made from lost technology...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:23.63,Default,JAYON,0,0,0,,If it has truly disappeared, this is more than\Njust a problem for the Bayrelicht Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:26.01,Default,EFILIA,0,0,0,,What about Schnee Raizar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:27.68,Default,EFILIA,0,0,0,,Do we know what happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:31.18,Default,CHANCELLOR,0,0,0,,We've been informed \Nshe's headed to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:35.38,Default,CHANCELLOR,0,0,0,,If that intel is correct,\Nshe should arrive sometime today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:38.19,Default,EFILIA,0,0,0,,Rionne still hasn't returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:41.32,Default,EFILIA,0,0,0,,We don't have enough information to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:44.99,Default,EFILIA,0,0,0,,Father, we should wait \Nfor Ms. Raizar's arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:47.94,Default,JAYON,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:52.70,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,Have you ever killed anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:53.67,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:57.83,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Sometimes you have to fight \Npeople on escort jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:01.85,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You're more likely to be attacked \Nby bandits than monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:09.22,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,Folks tend to underestimate me because \NI'm small, but I beat them all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.86,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,How dependable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:16.41,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I know. Things will be easier if we\Nknow what we're all capable of in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:19.32,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Why don't we briefly reintroduce ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:20.07,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:25.62,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,I am a samurai by trade. \NMy adventurer rank is A.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:29.12,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,I'm useless with magic, \Nso don't expect me to cast any spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:32.64,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,I'm a boxer. My rank is E.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:35.37,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,I can cast support spells to boost speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:39.94,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,I'm an alchemist, \Nbut I can use a bow and sword as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:43.58,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,I recently became an adventurer, \Nso I'm only rank G,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:46.26,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,but I can cast simple healing spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:48.89,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Let me know if you need one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:53.36,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Like Gaien, I'm a samurai. My rank is E.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:56.66,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I can cast a bit of fire and lightning magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:14:00.50,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,This is Yuzuha. Believe it or not,\N this little one's a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:02.73,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,We have a Tamer contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:07.85,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,A samurai who uses magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:10.66,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,You must've undergone some unusual training.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:14.17,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,And it's rare for monsters \Nto take a liking to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:16.67,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yuzuha is surprisingly strong, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:20.54,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,Are you originally from Hinomoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:24.05,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,No. What makes you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:27.32,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,Most samurai are from Hinomoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:30.00,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,You're the first one I've met besides Gaien.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.55,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Oh? You don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:35.34,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,Most people are warriors, \Nknights, or specialists.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:38.33,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,Those who become samurai\N tend to be the eccentric kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:40.18,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Eccentric?! Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:43.00,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It's a great profession that can do\Nit all, from tank to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:47.36,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,Like how knight and berserker \Nare prerequisites for the profession.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:48.52,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,It makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:50.20,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Oh, that's what you meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:54.05,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I get that, but to be blunt, we're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:57.50,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,I'll concede that much, but it's still weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:15:01.96,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,Indeed. Hinomoto, where most samurai \Nhail from, is a unique island nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:06.00,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,It was created by natural disaster
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:09.93,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,and is home to several samurai\Nand shinobi guild headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:14.27,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,The nation was built around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:17.50,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,Because of that, many who devote \Nthemselves to battle in Hinomoto
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:19.98,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,hold a special admiration for samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:23.57,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What are some of the guilds\N founded in Hinomoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:25.40,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,The most commonly known are
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:29.54,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,Kacho Fugetsu, Majin Keppuroku, \Nand Kuromiko Jinja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:31.11,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Wow, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:36.24,Italics,SHIN/ID,0,0,0,,I can't believe there's a whole country \Nbased around guilds from the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:41.37,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,There are other smaller guilds, \Nbut they aren't as famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:45.46,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Got it. Thanks for the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:48.63,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nakk?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:56.51,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Are you bandits?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:58.98,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mister Merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:03.27,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,If you don't wanna die, \Nleave all your money and cargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.98,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Nakk, get inside the wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:10.50,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yuzuha, defend Nakk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:18.66,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What should we do? \NThere aren't too many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:22.30,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,Should they attack us, \Nwe'll turn the tables on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:33.38,Flashback,GAIEN,0,0,0,,Have you ever killed anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:37.76,Italics,TIERA/ID,0,0,0,,I have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:41.89,Italics,TIERA/ID,0,0,0,,Otherwise, the others \Nwill be in greater danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:45.78,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,C'mon, now. You think the three\N of you can take us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:50.15,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,Why don't you leave the redhead, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:54.15,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,We're gonna have some fun with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:58.16,Default,BANDIT 2,0,0,0,,We'll make you scream and cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:02.16,Default,BANDIT 2,0,0,0,,I can't get excited unless I hear screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:06.54,Default,BANDIT 3,0,0,0,,Poor thing. He won't let you die quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:10.55,Default,BANDIT 3,0,0,0,,If anything, you'll be begging\N for him to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:14.55,Default,BANDIT 3,0,0,0,,Not that it'll change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:16.30,Italics,TIERA/ID,0,0,0,,Shin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:19.30,Italics,TIERA/ID,0,0,0,,He's not his usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.72,Italics,TIERA/ID,0,0,0,,I don't like this bloodlust.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:23.81,Italics,TIERA/ID,0,0,0,,I don't like this Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:33.74,Italics,TIERA/ID,0,0,0,,I'm scared to shoot someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:37.77,Italics,TIERA/ID,0,0,0,,but I have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:41.45,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,I don't enjoy needless killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:43.41,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,Retreat now, and you're free to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.58,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,But if you refuse, I'll cut you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:48.36,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,Come on. Don't you realize\Nthe position you're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:52.09,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,We know you've got a bunch\Nof E-rank and lower adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:59.54,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,You may be rank A, but you can't fight \Nwhile protecting the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:01.23,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,They know who we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:04.49,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,Sounds like this was no chance encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:07.16,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'm curious where they got that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:09.10,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,We'll beat it out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.37,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:11.70,Default,BANDIT 3,0,0,0,,This is getting to be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:14.40,Default,BANDIT 3,0,0,0,,Let's kill 'em all besides the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:17.70,Default,BANDIT 2,0,0,0,,They'll be quiet once they're corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:22.48,Default,ALL,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:27.08,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,How'd they spot our guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:35.58,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,Get 'em, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:41.85,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,Just you? You underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:44.37,Default,BANDIT 2,0,0,0,,Don't fight back too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:46.85,Default,BANDIT 2,0,0,0,,I can't have any fun with you if you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:48.73,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,You piss me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:54.36,Default,BANDIT 2,0,0,0,,Flashing Vigor? E-ranks shouldn't \Nbe able to use that technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:55.19,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,Fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:01.41,Default,BANDIT 3,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:04.28,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,Idiots! Don't take your eyes off them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:14.04,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,You'll die for this affront.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.83,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,That katana...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:22.80,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,Your swords seem to be magical, \Nbut unfortunately, so is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.40,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You're wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:34.19,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:37.57,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,Aside from the dragnir, \Naren't you all rank E or lower?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:42.07,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,We've got magic swords and should be \Nhigher level than you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:45.45,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What will you do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:50.85,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Let's get rid of that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:20:00.81,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Once I immobilize you, you're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:03.95,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,What? No, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:11.35,Default,NAKK,0,0,0,,I-Is it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:19.01,Default,GAIEN,0,0,0,,You went wild on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:20.86,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I was actually holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:23.86,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,You can't be serious. You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:25.66,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:28.24,Default,BANDIT 1,0,0,0,,You can't keep up that bravado for—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:34.10,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You're going to tell us \Nwhere you got your information.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:40.82,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Shin. Shin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:52.39,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,Uh, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.87,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Just give us a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:56.40,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Don't you move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:01.06,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,U-Um, Tiera?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:07.70,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Uh... What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:11.05,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,You're back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:15.07,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:21.70,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:22.95,Default,TSUBAKI,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:28.80,Italics,TIERA/ID,0,0,0,,What am I doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:34.99,Italics,TIERA/ID,0,0,0,,Shin seemed so cold and dark earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:40.61,Italics,TIERA/ID,0,0,0,,Did he realize it, or was it just me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.50,0:21:45.95,Italics,TIERA/ID,0,0,0,,It always calmed me down when\Nmy master did that for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:48.71,Italics,TIERA/ID,0,0,0,,so I did it to Shin on a whim, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.99,0:22:00.13,Default,TIERA,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to face him now?!
